ompartments through phase separation to\naccomplish relevant functions such as encapsulation of primitive metabolic,\ngenetic and catalytic materials, exchange of these materials, motion,\ncoalescence, and evolution. All of these functions can result in the gels'\ncapability to alter local geochemical niches on other planets, thereby allowing\nchemical evolution to lead to OoL events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 04:16:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-11"}
