ectively. The results\ndemonstrate the usefulness of the design of the scintillation tracker for the\nmuon track matching in the nuclear-emulsion-based neutrino-nucleus interaction\nmeasurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 08:57:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 May 2022 06:40:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-16"}
