esence of scavengers and/or in the absence of oxygen were also performed\naiming to characterize the most reactive species formed during the\nsemiconductor photo-activation process and thus assessing to possible reactive\npathways underpinning the photocatalytic activity of the hybrid C-dots/TNT\nnanomaterials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jan 2022 16:56:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 17:49:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-26"}
